tps://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-above-estimates-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾马科斯表示与特朗普通话时讨论了联盟问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-marcos-says-discussed-alliance-call-with-trump-2024-11-19/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯表示，他和美国候任总统唐纳德·特朗普在周二的电话中讨论了两国的联盟以及加强两国深厚关系的愿望。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 09:19:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-marcos-says-discussed-alliance-call-with-trump-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>印度钢铁制造商推出新的临时税收措施以遏制廉价进口产品</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indian-steelmakers-make-new-push-temporary-tax-check-cheap-imports-2024-11-19/</link><description>根据最新的行业报告，印度钢铁制造商敦促政府立即征收临时税，以阻止来自中国、日本和韩国的廉价进口，这是向新德里施压，限制廉价海外供应的新举措。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 09:16:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indian-steelmakers-make-new-push-temporary-tax-check-cheap-imports-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>普京以新核学说向美国发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/putin-issues-warning-us-with-new-nuclear-doctrine-2024-11-19/</link><description>据报道，白宫允许乌克兰向俄罗斯深处发射美国导弹几天后，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京周二降低了核打击的门槛，以应对更广泛的常规攻击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 08:46:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/putin-issues-warning-us-with-new-nuclear-doctrine-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>奥斯汀表示，美菲联盟将超越政府</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-defence-chief-says-treaty-with-philippines-covers-armed-attacks-south-china-2024-11-19/</link><description>美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀周二表示，美国与菲律宾的联盟将超越政府更迭，并重申了对这个东南亚国家的支持。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 06:33:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-defence-chief-says-treaty-with-philippines-covers-armed-attacks-south-china-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>新西兰准备收紧间谍法以阻止外国干涉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-prepares-tighten-espionage-laws-stop-foreign-interference-2024-11-19/</link><description>周二，新西兰通过了加强现有间谍法并引入新罪行的立法的第一个立法障碍。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 05:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-prepares-tighten-espionage-laws-stop-foreign-interference-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>伊朗、以色列等竞争对手将在越南国防博览会上展示武器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/iran-israel-among-rivals-showcase-their-arms-vietnam-defence-expo-2024-11-19/</link><description>越南国防部周二表示，来自伊朗、以色列、中国、俄罗斯和美国的公司将在 12 月于河内举行的军火博览会上展示军事装备，这是地缘政治竞争对手共同展示其产品的罕见案例。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 05:27:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/iran-israel-among-rivals-showcase-their-arms-vietnam-defence-expo-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>英国《金融时报》报道，欧盟要求中国企业进行技术转让</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-demand-tech-transfers-chinese-companies-ft-reports-2024-11-19/</link><description>英国《金融时报》周二援引两位欧盟高级官员的话报道称，欧盟正计划迫使中国企业向欧洲企业转让技术，以换取欧盟补贴。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 05:13:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-demand-tech-transfers-chinese-companies-ft-reports-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>G20领导人在里约峰会最后一天将焦点转向气候变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/g20-leaders-turn-focus-climate-change-rio-summits-last-day-2024-11-19/</link><description>领导人开会讨论可持续发展和向清洁能源过渡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 05:06:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/g20-leaders-turn-focus-climate-change-rio-summits-last-day-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯和中国外长在G20会议期间讨论关系、乌克兰和朝鲜半岛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-chinese-foreign-ministers-discuss-ties-ukraine-korean-peninsula-g20-2024-11-19/</link><description>两国外交部周二表示，中国和俄罗斯外长在巴西二十国集团会议期间讨论了双边关系、乌克兰冲突和朝鲜半岛局势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 04:50:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-chinese-foreign-ministers-discuss-ties-ukraine-korean-peninsula-g20-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>“香港47”：对民主人士入狱的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-47-reaction-jailings-democrats-landmark-national-security-trial-2024-11-19/</link><description>批评人士称，这是对金融中心法治的重大打击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 03:56:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-47-reaction-jailings-democrats-landmark-national-security-trial-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国外长会见印度外长呼吁恢复直航</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-foreign-minister-meets-indian-counterpart-calls-resumption-direct-flights-2024-11-19/</link><description>中国外交部周二发表声明称，中国外交部长王毅周一在里约热内卢会见了印度外长苏杰生，并呼吁恢复两国之间的直航。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 03:25:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-foreign-minister-meets-indian-counterpart-calls-resumption-direct-flights-2024-11-19/</guid></item></channel></rss>